---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title='Privacy Policy' description='Privacy policy for QuBrite.'>
	<main class='mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 prose dark:prose-invert'>
		<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

		<p>
			QuBrite is a static publication. We collect the minimum data needed to understand
			audience trends and improve editorial work, and we ask before storing anything beyond
			what is strictly required to load the site.
		</p>

		<h2>Cookies and consent</h2>

		<p>
			On your first visit we show a cookie notice. Until you choose, no analytics or
			advertising cookies are stored. You can change your choice at any time using the
			<strong>Cookie preferences</strong> link in the site footer.
		</p>

		<ul>
			<li>
				<strong>Essential:</strong> always on. Theme preference and basic site
				functionality.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics (GA4) measures aggregated, anonymized
				traffic patterns. IP anonymization is enabled. We do not sell this data.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Ads &amp; personalization:</strong> if enabled, advertising partners may
				use cookies for ads personalization and measurement under Google Consent Mode v2.
			</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Third parties</h2>

		<p>
			If affiliate links or advertising are used, third-party services may process data
			according to their own policies. We link to source material on the public web, which
			may set its own cookies if you click through.
		</p>

		<h2>Contact</h2>

		<p>
			Privacy questions: see the <a href='/contact/'>contact page</a>.
		</p>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>
